            <p>Built for scale, stability, and operational efficiency. No surprises when you go live.</p>
          </div>
        </TextReveal>

        <TextReveal delay={300} client:load>
          <div class="why-card">
            <div class="why-icon">üíµ</div>
            <h3>Cost-Optimized Architecture</h3>
            <p>Enterprise performance without enterprise costs. We optimize every layer of your AI stack.</p>
          </div>
        </TextReveal>

        <TextReveal delay={400} client:load>
          <div class="why-card">
            <div class="why-icon">üîí</div>
            <h3>Enterprise-Grade Security</h3>
